{"title":"Cadel Evans Convinces Bellroy to Re-release Fancy Leather All-Conditions Pockets","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bellroy-re-release-leather-pocket-organizer/","date":1680889978000,"content":"<p>The Australian <a href=\"https://bellroy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Carry Company</a>, Bellroy has re-released their fancy pre-molded leather All-Conditions Pockets. These “fan favorite”, waterproof pockets are pre-molded using water-resistant leather. They use an internal, organization system to keep things neat and tidy in your jersey pocket. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-Multi-tool-e1678120770639.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"726\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-Multi-tool-e1678120770639.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Phone Pocket Plus Multi tool\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-Multi-tool-e1678120770639.jpeg 726w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-Multi-tool-e1678120770639-297x129.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-Multi-tool-e1678120770639-120x52.jpeg 120w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Bellroy</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The All-Conditions Pocket comes in three sizes, All-Condition <a href=\"https://bellroy.com/products/all-conditions-card-pocket?color=ink&amp;material=leather_ripstop\" target=\"_blank\">Card </a>Pocket, All-Condition <a href=\"https://bellroy.com/products/all-conditions-phone-pocket?color=ink&amp;material=leather_ripstop&amp;size=standard\" target=\"_blank\">Phone </a>Pocket, and All-Condition <a href=\"https://bellroy.com/products/all-conditions-phone-pocket-plus?color=bronze&amp;material=leather&amp;size=plus\" target=\"_blank\">Phone Plus</a> Pocket. It would come in handy as a kind of “everyday carry” for some adventurers, people on the go, gym rats, cyclists, or anybody that likes to have their stuff tidy and organized. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-zipper-e1678121792722.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"355\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-zipper-e1678121792722.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Card Pocket zipper\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-zipper-e1678121792722.jpeg 730w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-zipper-e1678121792722-297x144.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-zipper-e1678121792722-120x58.jpeg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All of the All-Conditions Pocket products include a pre-molded water-resistant leather shell, and the Aquaguard Zipper to really help keep the water from getting in and ruining the goodies inside. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-Cadel-Evans-e1678120828280.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"436\" height=\"467\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-Cadel-Evans-e1678120828280.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Card Pocket Cadel Evans\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-Cadel-Evans-e1678120828280.jpeg 436w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-Cadel-Evans-e1678120828280-280x300.jpeg 280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-Cadel-Evans-e1678120828280-112x120.jpeg 112w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Bellroy’s Instagram. Cadel Evans (left) </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Bellroy claims that one of the biggest proponents of bringing back these handy lil’ pockets was Tour De France winner, Cadel Evans. They say that he “<em>has been one of the biggest fans (and loudest voices in convincing us to bring them back). He recently gifted a special edition of the pocket to the teams at his annual Great Ocean Road Race</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-black.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"487\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-black.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Card Pocket black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-black.jpeg 730w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-black-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-black-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-black-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>All-Conditions Card Pocket in Black</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-bronze.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"487\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-bronze.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Phone Pocket bronze\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-bronze.jpeg 730w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-bronze-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-bronze-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-bronze-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>All-Conditions Phone Pocket in Bronze</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-black.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"487\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-black.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Phone Pocket Plus black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-black.jpeg 730w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-black-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-black-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-black-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>All-Conditions Phone Pocket Plus in Black</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All three different sizes of the All-Condition Pockets come in either Black or Bronze colors and are backed with Bellroy’s 3-year warranty. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>All-Conditions Card Pocket</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-inside-e1678121516617.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"368\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-inside-e1678121516617.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Card Pocket inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-inside-e1678121516617.jpeg 730w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-inside-e1678121516617-297x150.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Card-Pocket-inside-e1678121516617-120x60.jpeg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://bellroy.com/products/all-conditions-card-pocket?color=ink&amp;material=leather_ripstop\" target=\"_blank\">All Conditions Card Pocket</a> is the smaller of the three sizes. Bellroy says it can hold up to 10 cards, folded bills, coins, keys, bike tools, and other “small EDC items”. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Retails for: $79</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Pre-molded water-resistant leather shell</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Water-resistant Aquaguard zipper</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Flexible storage for 10 cards, folded bills, coins, keys, and more.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Two internal stretch pockets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Raised coin and/or key pocket with key loop</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Backed by a 3-year warranty</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>All-Conditions Phone Pocket</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-inside-e1678122162892.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"728\" height=\"386\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-inside-e1678122162892.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Phone Pocket inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-inside-e1678122162892.jpeg 728w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-inside-e1678122162892-297x157.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-inside-e1678122162892-120x64.jpeg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://bellroy.com/products/all-conditions-phone-pocket?color=ink&amp;material=leather_ripstop&amp;size=standard\" target=\"_blank\">All Conditions Phone Pocket</a> sits in the middle of the three sizes. Bellroy says it can hold a standard smartphone, up to 2 cards, folded bills, and 2 keys. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Retails for: $109</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fits most standard smartphones. <em><strong>See the fit guide</strong></em> <em><strong>below</strong></em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pre-molded water-resistant leather shell</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Water-resistant Aquaguard zipper</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The stretch pocket keeps the phone secured</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Slip pockets hold a couple of cards</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The rear pocket holds folded bills</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Raised coin and/or key pocket with key loop</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Backed by a 3-year warranty</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>All-Conditions Phone Pocket Plus</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-inside-e1678122651966.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"719\" height=\"403\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-inside-e1678122651966.jpeg\" alt=\"Bellroy All-Conditions Phone Pocket Plus inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-inside-e1678122651966.jpeg 719w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-inside-e1678122651966-297x166.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-inside-e1678122651966-120x67.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-Plus-inside-e1678122651966-400x225.jpeg 400w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://bellroy.com/products/all-conditions-phone-pocket-plus?color=bronze&amp;material=leather&amp;size=plus\" target=\"_blank\">All Conditions Phone Pocket Plus</a> is the largest of the three sizes. Bellroy says it can hold a plus-sized smartphone, up to 2 cards, folded bills, and 2 keys. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Retails for: $119</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fits most plus-sized smartphones. <em><strong>See the fit guide</strong></em> <em><strong>below</strong></em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pre-molded water-resistant leather shell</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Water-resistant Aquaguard zipper</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The stretch pocket keeps the phone secured</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Slip pockets hold a couple of cards</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The rear pocket holds folded bills</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Raised coin and/or key pocket with key loop</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Backed by a 3-year warranty</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Phone Fit Guide</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For devices that are a tight fit, Bellroy recommends keeping your phone in the main section, rather than the mesh pocket. This makes zipping easier and reduces wear and tear.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-and-Pocket-Plus-phone-fit-guidejpg.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"661\" height=\"514\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-and-Pocket-Plus-phone-fit-guidejpg.jpg\" alt=\"Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-and-Pocket-Plus-phone-fit-guide.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-and-Pocket-Plus-phone-fit-guidejpg.jpg 661w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-and-Pocket-Plus-phone-fit-guidejpg-297x231.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bellroy-All-Conditions-Phone-Pocket-and-Pocket-Plus-phone-fit-guidejpg-120x93.jpg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p> Check out all of the carry options at the link below.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://bellroy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bellroy.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bellroy-re-release-leather-pocket-organizer/\">Cadel Evans Convinces Bellroy to Re-release Fancy Leather All-Conditions Pockets</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"bbcf0972db2557806a8cfc53da45b4920887b14f818c7def366b389edf566c8d","category":"Cycling"}